marketing: Shell Gadus S2 OG Clear Oil is formulated to minimise brass bearing and steel roller wear and maintain normal bearing temperatures under extreme operating conditions. Shell Gadus S2 OG Clear Oil incorporates synthetic thickeners and high viscosity mineral oils blended with extreme pressure additives to give a modern high performance sugar mill brass bearing lubricant.
